# Legacy root .env example
#
# The project has been split into two deployable services:
#
# 1. ops-core/.env.example
#    FastAPI ops core, project registry, SSH, SQLite, audit, notification push.
#
# 2. tg_schedule_bot/.env.example
#    Telegram adapter only. It calls ops-core through HTTP.
#
# Do not use this root file for new deployments. Copy the service-specific
# example instead:
#
#   cp ops-core/.env.example ops-core/.env
#   cp tg_schedule_bot/.env.example tg_schedule_bot/.env
